HEADWORD: Refocillate
<hw>Re*foc"il*late</hw> <pr>(r?*f?s"?l*l?t)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>refocillatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>refocillare</ets>; pref.
<ets>re-</ets> re- + <ets>focillare</ets> to revive by warmth.]</ety>
<def>To refresh; to revive.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Aubrey.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

